HDHRUtil-ChannelScan - Report status, or start or stop a channel scan


usage: HDHRUtil-ChannelScan [-h] --hdhr HDHR [--status | --start | --stop]
                            [--source SOURCE]

optional arguments:
  -h, --help       show this help message and exit
  --hdhr HDHR      the HDHomeRun to manage
  --status         status of the channel scan (default action)
  --start          start a channel scan
  --stop, --abort  stop a channel scan
  --source SOURCE  specify a source type



Scenerio:

You want to start a new channel scan

    HDHRUtil-ChannelScan --hdhr=myhdhr.local --start

You want to check the status of an ongoing scan

    HDHRUtil-ChannelScan --hdhr=myhdhr.local --status
